Name: EXE: Mainframe
About the game: EXE: Mainframe is a twin stick arcade shootem-up. You must survive as long as you can and compete for the highest score. You'll fight through an endless wave of enemies and collect power ups along the way as the difficulty increases. How long can you survive the mainframe?
